HEADWORD: Manucode
<hw>Man"u*code</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Javanese
<ets>manukdewata</ets> the bird of the gods: cf. F.
<ets>manucode</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any bird of the
genus <gen>Manucodia</gen>, of Australia and New Guinea. They are
related to the bird of paradise.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

